TWDT is launched by CryptoDT platform ,founded by Green World FinTech Service Co., Ltd, the largest third-party payment company in Taiwan.

Each TWDT is guaranteed to have an equivalent of NT$1 in the bank's trust account and is audited by professionals to ensure that it is permanently anchored to a non-fluctuating price : 1 TWDT= NT$1 .
